overview: ITC: Paranormal or Pareidolia takes a look at Instrumental Transcommunication or ITC showing various methods used to attempt to contact the Spirit world as well as informing that people different ideas when it comes to the efficacy of such methods. Please join us for an informative sojourn into the Paranormal.
tagline: Join us for this look into the world of Intstrumental Transcommunication.
title: ITC: Paranormal or Pareidolia
